---
description: Comic UI, CSS tokens, and motion conventions
globs:
  - src/components/**/*
  - src/styles/**/*
  - "**/*.module.css"
alwaysApply: false
---

# UI (comic)

- Style with co-located CSS Modules (`Component.module.css`) and tokens from `src/styles/`.
- Prefer existing `components/comic/*` primitives over new card/dashboard patterns.
- Colors/fonts: Persona red/black/cream tokens (`--color-red`, etc.) — do not introduce purple/SaaS defaults.
- Motion uses `motion` + `lib/motionPresets.ts` and respects `useAnimationProfile` / reduced-motion.
- Keep Spanish labels consistent with Navigation and shell chrome.
- No Tailwind; do not invent a parallel design system.
